    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Meticulously maintained, the high-revving straight-six is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains taut and precise. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with a flawless exterior and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear or trim degradation.",
