    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence: a 2021 Audi S5 Sportback in a breathtaking Glacier White Metallic finish. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and is in showroom-fresh, mint condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a deep, mirror-like gloss. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather interior remains supple and entirely free of wear, still retaining that new-car scent. Every feature, from the Bang & Olufsen 3D Sound System to the Audi Virtual Cockpit, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with all service performed exclusively by Audi certified technicians\u2014full service records are included. With zero door dings, no curb rash on the 19-inch 5-spoke-cavo design wheels, and a smoke-free/pet-free history, this S5 is for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 47500.0,
