    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolutely stunning shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch is spotless. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale, so I've priced it to be a total steal for someone who appreciates a ride in perfect condition. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
