    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional specimen of the S54-powered era, featuring the iconic 3.2L high-revving inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that operates flawlessly. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, driving power to the rear wheels through a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Suspension components retain their factory-spec damping, and the braking system provides immediate, linear deceleration. This is a true driver\u2019s car, maintained with obsessive attention to mechanical tolerances and fluid intervals.",
